{
  "stem": "7722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I heard the people working from me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they would be today alive they would say, you see, but I was 12 years old, or 13 years old-- my father never hit a child.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He told me, my son, if you want to be-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] if you are-- if-- if you want to be respected, respect all human beings, [SOBBING] regardless who he is.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we built the house, we built a big house, and we ran out of funds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father told me, you want to get rich, you eat bread and water, and the people who work for you, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] paid in time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you see, in Europe, was-- you could buy-- the merchants could buy a lot of things, could buy on note-- they gave notes on certain-- they called this a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They gave note.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "See, we used to pour kerosene, you had to pay cash.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For oil, and benzene, like-- because we had to-- we had to order a barrel in our town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we had in our town a big sugar factory, we had in our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had oil and everything to sell to them and gasoline.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And gasoline-- That's to the Ukrainians?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the [POLISH]-- in Polish, it wasn't a baron.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a-- they called this a [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was here, he was near it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a wealthy man, and he had a car-- he had cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was in our town a big sugar factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to make sugar from beets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the factory did belong to a famous Jewish-- Brotzky they called him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had-- all over Russia, he had sugar factories.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
